title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim Update 14 -  first beta build available
description:
In this video we will look at what has been added and what has been fixed in the first beta release for Sim Update 14 which will be released in a few weeks. The fix list contains both fixes for aircrafts but also some stability/performance fixes. As a bonus some new functionality will be added to the ATC.
